Subject: [PATCH] iio: health: max30102: Add power enable parameter to get_temp function
Git-commit: a9c47abbdd71dceeaf1b923e5ce10e700e036905
Patch-mainline: v4.16-rc1
References: bsc#1051510

Chip must not be in shutdown for reading temperature, so briefly leave
shutdown if buffer is not already running

